1177
01:06:44.960 --> 01:06:49.440
Like. if all of us had to provide evidence
for two soulmates. we'd all pick you two.

1178
01:06:49.960 --> 01:06:52.480
-There's no such thing as soulmates.
-Maybe.

1179
01:06:53.000 --> 01:06:55.760
